                書記官　游秀珠\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　3 　　月　　9 　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c4515%2c20210309%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,上訴,4515,20210309,2","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"4515","JDATE":"20210309","JTITLE":"違反森林法等"}